# Terraform working data and sensitive state
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
*.plan
backend.hcl
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# Terraform variable files can contain account-specific or secret values
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json
!*.example.tfvars

# Local environment and secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx

# Kubernetes and local cluster access
kubeconfig
kubeconfig.*
*.kubeconfig

# AWS and container authentication must never be copied into the repository
.aws/
.docker/

# Generated Helm and Kubernetes files containing local values
secrets*.yaml
secrets*.yml
*-secret.yaml
*-secret.yml

# IDE and operating-system files
.idea/
.vscode/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Local logs and temporary output
*.log
tmp/
temp/

# Private career/interview materials must never be committed or pushed
docs/interview-guide.md
docs/interview-preparation*.md
docs/*interview*.md
docs/star-stories.md
docs/*star*.md
docs/linkedin-post.md
docs/*linkedin*.md
docs/resume-bullets.md
docs/*resume*.md
docs/*cv*.md
docs/personal-notes*.md
docs/recruiter*.md
docs/job-application*.md
private/
private-docs/
career/
interview/
linkedin/
resume/

# Python development artifacts
.venv/
venv/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
